title: EU Should Not Listen to US, NATO to Resolve Domestic Crises
text: The European Union is gradually turning into a big loser of the Syrian war in the international arena. Over the last year, a number of tendencies have emerge which could erode the legitimacy of the bloc and reverse the integration process, an article for the Portugal media outlet Publico read. ...
